# Hakim Car Service - Design Guidelines

## Color Palette
- Primary Color: #FFD700 (Yellow)
- Secondary Color: #FFE44D (Light Yellow)
- Primary Gray: #2C3E50 (Dark Blue-Gray)
- Secondary Gray: #95A5A6 (Light Gray)
- Primary Black: #1A1A1A
- White: #FFFFFF
- Light Gray: #F5F6FA

## Typography
- Primary Font: Inter
- Fallback Fonts: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif
- Font Sizes:
  - h1: 3.5rem (2.5rem on mobile)
  - h2: 2.5rem (2rem on mobile)
  - h3: 1.75rem (1.5rem on mobile)
  - Body: 1rem
  - Small Text: 0.9rem

## Spacing
- Container Max Width: 1200px
- Section Padding: 6rem 0 (4rem 0 on mobile)
- Container Padding: 0 2rem (0 1rem on mobile)
- Button Padding: 1rem 2rem (0.875rem 1.75rem on mobile)
- Grid Gap: 2.5rem
- Card Padding: 2rem

## Components

### Buttons
- Primary Button:
  - Background: var(--primary-yellow)
  - Text: var(--primary-black)
  - Border: none
  - Border Radius: var(--border-radius)
  - Box Shadow: var(--box-shadow)
  - Hover: 
    - Background: var(--secondary-yellow)
    - Transform: translateY(-2px)
    - Box Shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)

- Secondary Button:
  - Background: transparent
  - Border: 2px solid var(--primary-gray)
  - Text: var(--primary-gray)
  - Border Radius: var(--border-radius)
  - Hover:
    - Background: var(--primary-gray)
    - Text: var(--white)
    - Transform: translateY(-2px)
    - Box Shadow: var(--box-shadow)

### Cards
- Background: white
- Border Radius: 1rem
- Box Shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)
- Padding: 2rem
- Hover:
  - Transform: translateY(-5px)
  - Box Shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)
  - Background: #FFD700
  - Text Color: #000

### Navigation
- Header Height: 80px
- Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95)
- Box Shadow: var(--box-shadow)
- Backdrop Filter: blur(10px)
- Logo Color: var(--primary-yellow)
- Menu Items:
  - Color: var(--primary-gray)
  - Hover: Underline animation with var(--primary-yellow)

### Icons
- Size: 2.5rem
- Color: var(--primary-yellow)
- Hover: 
  - Color: #000
  - Transform: scale(1.1)

## Animations
- Transition: all 0.3s ease
- Hover Effects:
  - Scale: 1.1
  - TranslateY: -2px to -5px
  - Box Shadow: Enhanced on hover

## Layout
- Grid System: CSS Grid with auto-fit
- Responsive Breakpoints:
  - Mobile: < 768px
  - Tablet: 768px - 1024px
  - Desktop: > 1024px

## Hero Section
- Background: Linear gradient (135deg, var(--primary-yellow) 0%, var(--secondary-yellow) 100%)
- Pattern Overlay: url('/images/pattern.svg') with 0.1 opacity
- Min Height: 100vh
- Text Color: var(--primary-gray)

## Services Section
- Background: var(--light-gray)
- Grid: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr))
- Card Hover: Yellow background with black text

## CTA Section
- Background: var(--primary-gray)
- Text Color: var(--white)
- Pattern Overlay: url('/images/pattern.svg') with 0.05 opacity

## Footer
- Background: var(--primary-gray)
- Text Color: var(--white)
- Section Headers: var(--primary-yellow)
- Grid: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr))
- Padding: 6rem 0 2rem

## Accessibility
- Color Contrast: WCAG 2.1 AA compliant
- Focus States: Visible outline
- Alt Text: Required for images
- ARIA Labels: Required for interactive elements

## Loading States
- Skeleton Loading: var(--light-gray) background
- Spinner: var(--primary-yellow)
- Duration: 300ms

## Error States
- Error Message: var(--primary-gray)
- Error Border: 2px solid var(--primary-yellow)
- Error Icon: Required

## Success States
- Success Message: var(--primary-gray)
- Success Icon: Required
- Duration: 3000ms

## Images
- Avatar: 40px x 40px
- Thumbnail: 120px x 120px
- Hero: 1920px x 600px
- Format: WebP with PNG fallback 